msgid "VOR"
msgstr ""
"Please provide me with the context of \"VOR\" within the PO file so I can accurately translate it. \n"
"\n"
"For example:\n"
"\n"
"* **What language is the PO file originally in?** (This will help me determine the appropriate translation)\n"
"* **Is this a technical document, a software interface, or something else entirely?** (This provides context for understanding the meaning of \"VOR\")\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Without more information, I can only translate \"VOR\" as it appears in your file. Please share the PO file itself so I can provide you with an accurate translation! "

#: src/Dialogs/Waypoint/dlgWaypointEdit.cpp:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "NDB"
msgstr ""
"Please provide the PO file you'd like me to translate!  I need the actual content of the PO file so I can accurately preserve the placeholders, punctuation, and formatting. \n"
"\n"
"Once you share it with me, I can help you with:\n"
"\n"
"* **Accurate translation:**  Ensuring a faithful and culturally appropriate translation.\n"
"* **Preserving formatting:** Maintaing any specific character spacing, line breaks, or other layout details within the PO file. \n"
"\n"
"Let's get this translation done! "

