"Please provide me with the context of \"TC 30s\". \n"
"\n"
"I need to know what language the PO file is originally in and what it's supposed to translate.  \n"
"\n"
"For example:\n"
"\n"
"* **Is this a translation file for software?** If so, please let me know if there's any specific text you want translated or if you can share the context of the file.\n"
